Học Cùng Teacher Tom to Everyone (9:58 PM)
Step 1: find “.active” (or “.show”) container => remove “.show” class then add “.hidden”
Step 2: find the correct container (e.g: “#image-container”) => add class “.show” then remove class “.hidden”
